**Beta handoff verification**

- Finalized the beta handoff verifier in scripts/verification/check_beta_handoff_bundle.sh.
- Removed the graph health gate from the beta handoff bundle in Codexify-Beta/README.md, Codexify-Beta/docker-compose.yml, and docs/beta/2026-04-30-local-beta-release-evidence.md.
